    "image_with_text_BGNU9Q": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Womens-Rashvest-The-Aceh-Crop-Rash-Vest-Ocean-Soul-Bali-11.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Choose an Ocean Soul Women’s Rash Vest?",
        "text": "<p>Our women’s rash vests are designed by and for ocean-loving women who want protection without compromise. Here’s why they’re different:</p><h4> Superior Sun Protection</h4><p>Every women’s rash guard in our collection is rated UPF 50+, blocking 98% of UVA and UVB rays. Perfect for long surf sessions, snorkeling adventures, or beach days, they keep your skin protected naturally — without heavy sunscreens or chemical finishes.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_bVg7EM": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/womens-rashguard-mentawai-crop-top-ocean-soul-bali-sustainable-swimwear-234854.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable, Ethical, and Built to Last",
        "text": "<p>Our eco rash vests are made from ECONYL® regenerated nylon, a fabric created from ocean waste like discarded fishing nets and industrial plastics. Every piece is sewn in Bali by skilled local makers under ethical working conditions.</p><p>We produce in small batches to minimise waste and ensure superior quality, resulting in a garment that lasts up to twice as long as conventional surfwear.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_pkr9Tw": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/womens-rashguard-mentawai-crop-top-crop-rash-vest-ocean-soul-bali-4.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable, Ethical, and Built to Last",
        "text": "<p>Our eco rash vests are made from ECONYL® regenerated nylon, a fabric created from ocean waste like discarded fishing nets and industrial plastics. Every piece is sewn in Bali by skilled local makers under ethical working conditions.</p><p>We produce in small batches to minimise waste and ensure superior quality, resulting in a garment that lasts up to twice as long as conventional surfwear.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_4nGtbT": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/womens-rashvest-the-aceh-ocean-soul-bali-sustainable-swimwear-164785.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Performance Fit That Stays Put",
        "text": "<p>We’ve tested our rash vests in the waves, and they’re built to move with you - not against you. The sculpted panelling supports your natural shape while ensuring the top stays secure through every paddle and pop-up.</p><p>Streamlined seams to reduce drag and chafing<br/></p><p>Four-way stretch for unrestricted motion<br/></p><p>Longer body length to prevent ride-up<br/></p><p>Hidden thumbholes on select designs for extra hold and coverage<br/></p><p>Whether you’re pairing it with our surf bathing suits or wearing it solo, your Ocean Soul rash guard will stay perfectly in place.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_DJmA74": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/women-rash-guard-the-sumba-crop-rash-vest-ocean-soul-bali-midnight-xxs-13.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Flattering Design, Feminine Details",
        "text": "<p>We know how hard it can be to find a women’s rashvest that’s both flattering and functional - so we built ours to do both. Our design features:</p><p>Contoured panelling that defines the waist<br/></p><p>Soft, sculpting recycled fabric that smooths and supports<br/></p><p>Secure, high neckline for added sun protection<br/></p><p>Double lining for comfort and opacity<br/></p><p>From the lineup to lounging, these tops look as elegant as they perform.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
