        "text_block_kWNTkk": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Style It Your Way",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Our rash vests are versatile enough to wear on any adventure:</p><p>Surf-Ready: Layer over your surf bikini top or high-waisted bikini bottoms for total coverage.<br/></p><p>Beach to Brunch: Pair with women’s jogger pants or a resort sarong for a polished, sun-safe look.<br/></p><p>Travel-Friendly: Lightweight, packable, and quick-drying - perfect for coastal getaways.<br/></p><p></p>",
