            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Explore our full range of women’s rash vests and long sleeve rashguards, crafted for performance, sustainability, and style.</p><p>Pair them with:</p><p>One Piece Swimwear for streamlined surf protection<br/></p><p>High-Waisted Bikini Bottoms for sculpting comfort<br/></p><p>Surf Bikini Tops for total freedom and flexibility<br/></p><p>Resort Sarongs or Wide-Leg Lounge Pants for effortless après-surf style<br/></p><p>Each piece is sustainably made, ethically produced, and designed to move with you - from surf to shore.</p><p>Ocean Soul Swimwear - where protection meets performance, and style meets sustainability.</p>",
